{
  "title": "Sweet And Dense French Egg Salad",
  "description": "This halal-friendly sweet and dense egg salad is perfect for a solo dinner. It combines sous-vide cooked eggs with flour to achieve its signature texture.",
  "cuisine": "French",
  "diet": [
